</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[984,1075,1857,1883]" pageId="41" pageNumber="42" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, ♂, holotype (MPEG 0110). 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,210,1891,1917]" pageId="41" pageNumber="42">A</emphasis>
. Prosoma (dorsal view). 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[492,511,1891,1917]" pageId="41" pageNumber="42">B</emphasis>
. Prosoma (ventral view). 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[804,825,1891,1917]" pageId="41" pageNumber="42">C</emphasis>
